Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
“What’s Going On, New Haven” is our newest and most creative means to share and engage residents, friends and family of the community in whats new and entertaining in The Village. Additional information can also be found on our website at www.VillageofNewHaven.org under Sub menu Parks & Recreation or Email New Haven Parks and Recreation directly at: pr@villageofnewhaven-mi.gov

Developed By: N.E. Sawka
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
